===[[Pokémon Masters EX]]===
{{main|Hugh (Masters)}}
Hugh forms a [[sync pair]] with {{p|Bouffalant}}, {{p|Unfezant}}, and {{p|Pignite}} in [[Pokémon Masters EX]]. Hugh became a playable sync pair on November 7, 2022.

Hugh first appeared as an NPC during the [[story event]] [[Revel in Rivalry]]. He has also made notable appearances in one of the game's main stories, the [[villain arc]].

